short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Armaria is a fast, open, and local first bookmarks manager.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Armaria is a FOSS bookmarks manager that keeps all of your local bookmarks in a SQLite database. You can use many different frontends to manage your bookmarks including browsers, and back them up and/or sync them however you see fit.
